org.apache.lucene.spatial3d.geom

Interface GeoBBox

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GeoArea, GeoMembershipShape, GeoOutsideDistance, GeoShape, GeoSizeable, Membership
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeoDegenerateVerticalLine

    public interface GeoBBox
extends GeoMembershipShape, GeoSizeable, GeoArea
    All bounding box shapes have this interface in common. This describes methods that bounding boxes have above and beyond GeoMembershipShape's.
    WARNING: This API is experimental and might change in incompatible ways in the next release.
